.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-list \- list outbound payments from the node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-list
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.RB [ --status
.IR pending | complete | failed ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists outbound payments from the CLN daemon via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR listpays .
Returns a JSON array:
.nf
[{
  "payment_hash": "<hex>",
  "bolt11": "lnbc...",
  "amount_msat": <int>,
  "amount_sat": <int>,
  "fee_msat": <int>,
  "status": "pending|complete|failed",
  "destination": "<pubkey>",
  "completed_at": <unix-ts|null>
}, ...]
.fi
.TP
.B --limit N
Return at most N payments (default 50, max 500).
.TP
.B --status complete|pending|failed
Filter by status.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (returns empty array if daemon unavailable).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1)
